# Animated Card Opening

An interactive **Animated Card Opening effect** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.
This project creates a smooth animation where a card opens when the user clicks or hovers over it. It can be used for greeting cards, invitations, product reveals, or interactive UI components.

## ✨ Features

* Smooth card opening animation
* Responsive design
* Lightweight and fast
* Easy to customize
* Works on all modern browsers

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3 (Animations & Transitions)
* JavaScript

## 📂 Project Structure

```
animated-card/
│
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── README.md
```

## 🚀 How to Use

1. Download or clone the repository.

```
git clone https://github.com/hasan56790/animated-cards.git
```

2. Open the project folder.

3. Run **index.html** in your browser.

## 🎨 Customization

You can easily customize:

* Card colors
* Animation speed
* Card size
* Content inside the card

Modify the **style.css** file to change the animation or design.

## 📌 Example Use Cases

* Digital greeting cards
* Invitation cards
* Product reveal cards
* Portfolio UI components

